- module_ctrl3: Control Module 3 (Components that are part of the module: ctrl3_switch, ctrl3_green_led, ctrl3_green_resistor, ctrl3_cable_in_pos, ctrl3_cable_in_neg, ctrl3_cable_out_pos, ctrl3_cable_out_neg)
